# ║   ██║     ██║   ██║██║   ██║██╔══██╗██║ ██╔╝██╔════╝████╗  ██║██╔════╝    ║
# ║   ██║     ██║   ██║██║   ██║██████╔╝█████╔╝ ███████╗██╔██╗ ██║███████╗    ║
# ║   ██║     ██║   ██║╚██╗ ██╔╝██╔══██╗██╔═██╗ ╚════██║██║╚██╗██║╚════██║    ║
# ║   ███████╗╚██████╔╝ ╚████╔╝ ██║  ██║██║  ██╗███████║██║ ╚████║███████║    ║
# ║   ╚══════╝ ╚═════╝   ╚═══╝  ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚══════╝    ║
# ║                                                                            ║
# ║                          Skye's Custom Scripts                             ║
